She served the Gu family for years.

23
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:23,460
She worked hard
even if she didn't achieve anything.

24
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,080
Now that she lost her tongue,

25
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,820
