for her to make a living.

26
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,199
Let's help her

27
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,680
as much as we can.

28
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:35,000
No wonder the servants
praise you for your generosity.

29
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:36,919
She set you up.

30
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:38,919
Don't you hate her?

31
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,599
Haven't you

32
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,680
