33
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,680
I was able to make a decision

34
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:47,930
because you have
solid reasons and evidence.

35
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:52,879
When

36
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,159
I was in Ping City,

37
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:57,599
I bear the stigma
of being the daughter of a murderer.

38
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,080
The old maids and servants

39
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,280
around me

40
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,639
bullied me,

41
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,240
so

42
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,400
I was prepared

43
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,919
for these.

44
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,159
Madam Li was wrong

45
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,240
to set you up.

46
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,800
But did the incense explode

47
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:21,520
because Father and Mother were mad?

48
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:23,599
Maybe.

49
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:26,439
Or maybe something's wrong
with the incense Madam Li gave me.

50
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,520
What do you think?

51
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:30,280
Huaizhou.

52
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:31,360
Qianyu.

53
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,280
Huaizhou.

54
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,719
Qianyu just returned to Hu City.

55
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,390
It's boring for her
to stay at home alone.

56
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,319
Why not

57
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,120
let Qianyu hold a ball

58
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,560
and let everyone has some fun?

59
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:44,719
Sure.

60
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,439
Thanks for thinking of me.

61
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,439
Huaizhou.

62
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,680
Don't worry.

63
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,560
