109
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,199
Mr. Gu.

110
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,920
Sitang, you're here.

111
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,199
Didn't I inform you?

112
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,490
Didn't you say you're not coming?

113
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,990
Didn't you write to me
that the Gu family wants to use the ball

114
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,270
