that I return to my own home?

132
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:18,150
You...

133
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,800
Sitang.

134
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,120
Don't be rude.

135
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,759
Gu Manor will always be Jingzhou's home.

136
